msgid "A new version is available!"
msgstr "发现有新版本！"

msgid "About"
msgstr "关于"

msgid "Accent color"
msgstr "强调色"

msgid ""
"Adjust layout, typography, transition timing, shadows, and inject custom CSS var"
"iables or rules when the built-in controls are not enough."
msgstr "调整布局、排版、过渡动画时间、阴影，并在内置控件不足时注入自定义 CSS 变量或规则。"

msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "高级"

msgid "and {count} more…"
msgstr "和 {count} 个更多..."

msgid ""
"Animate the active underline when switching between native LuCI tabs and themed "
"tab menus."
msgstr "在切换原生 LuCI 标签页和主题化标签菜单时，为活动下划线添加动画。"

msgid "Animation"
msgstr "动画"

msgid ""
"API rate limit exceeded. Please enter a GitHub Token to continue. This token is "
"only used for frontend requests and will not be saved on the router backend."
msgstr "API 调用频率已达上限。请输入 GitHub Token 以继续。此 token 只用于前端请求，不会保存在路由器后端。"

msgid ""
"Applies to standard buttons, inputs, selects, and similar form controls across t"
"he theme."
msgstr "适用于整个主题中的标准按钮、输入框、选择框及类似表单控件。"

msgid "Author"
msgstr "作者"

msgid "Backdrop blur radius"
msgstr "背景模糊半径"

msgid "Backend (GHProxy Acceleration)"
msgstr "后端 (GHProxy 加速)"

msgid "Backend (Official GitHub)"
msgstr "后端 (官方 GitHub)"

msgid "Base font size"
msgstr "基础字体大小"

msgid "Blur radius in pixels behind the login card in dark mode. Use 0 to disable blur."
msgstr "深色模式下，登录卡片背后的模糊半径（单位：像素）。使用 0 可禁用模糊效果。"

msgid ""
"Blur radius in pixels behind the login card in light mode. Use 0 to disable blur"
"."
msgstr "亮色模式下，登录卡片背后的模糊半径（单位：像素）。使用 0 可禁用模糊效果。"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgid "Card background"
msgstr "卡片背景"

msgid "Card shadow"
msgstr "卡片阴影"

msgid "Check for updates"
msgstr "检查更新"

msgid "Checking for updates..."
msgstr "正在检查更新..."

msgid "Choose color"
msgstr "选择颜色"

msgid "Color mode"
msgstr "色彩模式"

msgid "Colors"
msgstr "颜色"

msgid "Comfortable (42px)"
msgstr "舒适（42px）"

msgid "Compact (32px)"
msgstr "紧凑（32px）"

msgid ""
"Configure color mode, accent colors, layout sizing, animation behavior, login-pa"
"ge appearance, and advanced CSS overrides for luci-theme-fluent."
msgstr "配置色彩模式、强调色、布局尺寸、动画行为、登录页面外观，以及用于 `luci-theme-fluent` 的高级 CSS 覆盖。"

msgid "Confirm Installation"
msgstr "确认安装"

msgid "Continue"
msgstr "继续"

msgid "Control height"
msgstr "控件高度"

msgid "Choose the document direction for authenticated and login pages. Automatic mode resolves Arabic and Persian locale codes (ar, ar_*, ar-*, fa, fa_*, fa-*) to RTL and falls back to LTR for missing or unrecognized locales."
msgstr "为已登录页面和登录页面选择文档方向。自动模式会将阿拉伯语和波斯语语言环境代码（ar、ar_*、ar-*、fa、fa_*、fa-*）解析为 RTL，对于缺失或无法识别的语言环境则回退为 LTR。"

msgid ""
"Controls the font weight used by main navigation labels and related theme text a"
"ccents."
msgstr "控制主导航标签及相关主题强调文本的字体粗细。"

msgid ""
"Controls the shared Fluent corner radius tokens used by cards, buttons, inputs, "
"and related UI surfaces."
msgstr "控制卡片、按钮、输入框及相关 UI 元素共享的 Fluent 圆角半径值。"

msgid ""
"Controls the shared Fluent transition timing used by menu, header, and other the"
"me animations."
msgstr "控制菜单、头部和其他主题动画中使用的共享 Fluent 过渡时间。"

msgid "Corner radius"
msgstr "圆角半径"

msgid "Custom CSS"
msgstr "自定义 CSS"

msgid ""
"Customize the login page background, card opacity, and blur radius for light and"
" dark modes."
msgstr "自定义亮色模式和深色模式下登录页面的背景、卡片不透明度和模糊半径。"

msgid "Dark mode"
msgstr "深色模式"

msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "禁用"

msgid ""
"Display the themed loading indicator at the top edge during page loads and trans"
"itions."
msgstr "在页面加载和过渡期间，在顶部边缘显示主题化的加载指示器。"

msgid "Download and Install"
msgstr "下载并安装"

msgid "Downloading on router"
msgstr "正在路由器上下载..."

msgid "Enable page transition animation"
msgstr "启用页面过渡动画"

msgid "Enable tab underline animation"
msgstr "启用标签页下划线动画"

msgid "Expecting: %s"
msgstr "预期：%s"

msgid "Extra large (12px)"
msgstr "超大 (12像素)"

msgid "Failed to check for updates"
msgstr "检查更新失败"

msgid "Failed to fetch current theme version."
msgstr "未能获取当前主题版本。"

msgid "Fast"
msgstr "快速"

msgid "Finished"
msgstr "完成"

msgid "Fluent Design 2 theme for LuCI"
msgstr "适用于 LuCI 的 Fluent Design 2 主题"

msgid "Fluent theme settings"
msgstr "Fluent 主题设置"

msgid "Follow system"
msgstr "跟随系统"

msgid "Force LTR"
msgstr "强制 LTR"

msgid "Force RTL"
msgstr "强制 RTL"

msgid "Force dark mode"
msgstr "强制深色模式"

msgid "Force light mode"
msgstr "强制亮色模式"

msgid "General"
msgstr "常规"

msgid "Text direction"
msgstr "文本方向"

msgid "Automatic (Arabic/Persian locales only)"
msgstr "自动（仅阿拉伯语/波斯语语言环境）"

msgid "GitHub Token Required"
msgstr "需要 GitHub Token"

msgid "Header height"
msgstr "头部高度"

msgid "Height of the top header bar in pixels."
msgstr "顶部标题栏的高度，单位为像素。"

msgid ""
"HEX color used as the primary Fluent accent when the interface is rendered in da"
"rk mode."
msgstr "在界面以深色模式渲染时，用作 Fluent 主要强调色的十六进制颜色。"

msgid ""
"HEX color used as the primary Fluent accent when the interface is rendered in li"
"ght mode."
msgstr "在界面以亮色模式渲染时，用作 Fluent 主要强调色的十六进制颜色。"

msgid "HEX color used for container/card elements in dark mode."
msgstr "在深色模式下，用于容器/卡片元素的十六进制颜色。"

msgid "HEX color used for container/card elements in light mode."
msgstr "在亮色模式下，用于容器/卡片元素的十六进制颜色。"

msgid ""
"HEX color used for progress-bar labels while the interface is rendered in dark m"
"ode."
msgstr "在界面以深色模式渲染时，用于进度条标签的十六进制颜色。"

msgid ""
"HEX color used for progress-bar labels while the interface is rendered in light "
"mode."
msgstr "在界面以亮色模式渲染时，用于进度条标签的十六进制颜色。"

msgid "HEX color used for the main page background in dark mode."
msgstr "在深色模式下，用于主页面的背景的十六进制颜色。"

msgid "HEX color used for the main page background in light mode."
msgstr "在亮色模式下，用于主页面的背景的十六进制颜色。"

msgid "HEX color used for the navigation sidebar in dark mode."
msgstr "深色模式下导航侧边栏使用的十六进制颜色。"

msgid "HEX color used for the navigation sidebar in light mode."
msgstr "亮色模式下导航侧边栏使用的十六进制颜色。"

msgid "Installation cancelled by user."
msgstr "用户已取消安装。"

msgid "Installed version"
msgstr "已安装版本"

msgid "Installing package"
msgstr "正在安装软件包"

msgid "Large"
msgstr "大号"

msgid "Large (8px)"
msgstr "大号 (8px)"

msgid "Light mode"
msgstr "亮色模式"

msgid "Login"
msgstr "登录"

msgid "Login card opacity"
msgstr "登录卡片不透明度"

msgid "Login page"
msgstr "登录页"

msgid "Medium"
msgstr "中号"

msgid "Medium (4px)"
msgstr "中号 (4px)"

msgid "Navigation font weight"
msgstr "导航字体粗细"

msgid "Next"
msgstr "下一步"

msgid "Nightly build available (reinstallation check)."
msgstr "有夜间构建可用（检查是否需要重新安装）。"

msgid "Nightly Channel (Prerelease)"
msgstr "夜间版本通道 (预发布)"

msgid "No matching package asset found for your system architecture in this release."
msgstr "在此版本中，未找到适用于您系统架构的软件包资源。"

msgid "None"
msgstr "无"

msgid "Normal"
msgstr "常规"

msgid ""
"Opacity of the login card in dark mode. 0 is fully transparent and 1 is fully op"
"aque."
msgstr "深色模式下登录卡片的不透明度。0 表示完全透明，1 表示完全不透明。"

msgid ""
"Opacity of the login card in light mode. 0 is fully transparent and 1 is fully o"
"paque."
msgstr "亮色模式下登录卡片的不透明度。0 表示完全透明，1 表示完全不透明。"

msgid ""
"Optional raw CSS injected into the Fluent header template. Use this for extra --"
"fluent-* variable overrides or page-specific tweaks that are not exposed as dedi"
"cated options."
msgstr "在 Fluent 头部模板中注入可选的原始 CSS。用于额外的 `--fluent-*` 变量覆盖，或页面特定的调整，这些调整没有作为专门的选项暴露。"

msgid "Package format"
msgstr "软件包格式"

msgid "Page background"
msgstr "页面背景"

msgid "Please enter your password."
msgstr "请输入您的密码。"

msgid "Please enter your username."
msgstr "请输入您的用户名。"

msgid "Progress bar text color"
msgstr "进度条文本颜色"

msgid "Reload Web Interface"
msgstr "重新加载网页界面"

msgid "Replace native select elements with the theme's custom dropdown widget."
msgstr "使用主题的自定义下拉组件替换原生的选择元素。"

msgid "Respect reduced-motion preference"
msgstr "遵循减少动态效果偏好设置"

msgid "Retrying with token..."
msgstr "正在使用令牌重试..."

msgid "Rounded (6px)"
msgstr "圆角 (6px)"

msgid "Search menu items"
msgstr "搜索菜单项"

msgid "Search menu…"
msgstr "搜索菜单…"

msgid "Select the shadow depth applied to themed cards and panels."
msgstr "选择应用于主题卡片和面板的阴影深度。"

msgid "Semibold"
msgstr "半粗体"

msgid ""
"Sets the base interface font size in pixels. Most theme text scales from this va"
"lue through the Fluent CSS variables. Recommended range: 12-18px."
msgstr "设置基础界面字体大小（像素）。大多数主题文本会根据 Fluent CSS 变量从该值进行缩放。建议范围：12-18px。"

msgid "Show top loading bar"
msgstr "显示顶部加载条"

msgid "Sidebar background"
msgstr "侧边栏背景"

msgid "Sidebar width"
msgstr "侧边栏宽度"

msgid "Slow"
msgstr "慢速"

msgid "Small"
msgstr "小号"

msgid "Small (2px)"
msgstr "小号 (2px)"

msgid "Software Update"
msgstr "软件更新"

msgid "Source code"
msgstr "源代码"

msgid "Square (0px)"
msgstr "方形 (0px)"

msgid "Stable Channel"
msgstr "稳定版本通道"

msgid "Starting backend download..."
msgstr "开始后端下载..."

msgid "Starting update process..."
msgstr "启动更新过程..."

msgid "Submit"
msgstr "提交"

msgid "Switch theme mode"
msgstr "切换主题模式"

msgid ""
"The theme is being installed on your router. The logs are displayed below. Reloa"
"ding the web interface will apply the changes once RPCD restarts."
msgstr "主题正在安装到您的路由器。日志显示在下方。重新加载网页界面将在 RPCD 重启后应用更改。"

msgid ""
"The theme package is ready. Are you sure you want to proceed with the installati"
"on?"
msgstr "主题软件包已准备好。您确定要继续安装吗？"

msgid ""
"The token does NOT require any permissions/scopes to be granted (read-only publi"
"c access is sufficient)."
msgstr "该令牌不需要授予任何权限/范围（读取公共访问权限就足够了）。"

msgid "Theme settings"
msgstr "主题设置"

msgid ""
"Theme successfully updated! Reloading RPC service, please refresh the page in 5 "
"seconds."
msgstr "主题更新成功！正在重新加载 RPC 服务，请在 5 秒后刷新页面。"

msgid "Theme transition speed"
msgstr "主题过渡速度"

msgid "Triggering installation on router..."
msgstr "触发路由器上的安装..."

msgid "Update channel"
msgstr "更新通道"

msgid "Update failed"
msgstr "更新失败"

msgid "Upgrade Successful!"
msgstr "升级成功！"

msgid "Use Fluent custom select dropdowns"
msgstr "使用 Fluent 自定义下拉选择框"

msgid ""
"Use the browser View Transition API to animate navigation between LuCI pages whe"
"n supported."
msgstr "当浏览器支持时，使用浏览器的 View Transition API 为 LuCI 页面之间的导航添加过渡动画。"

msgid ""
"Use the system/browser preference, or always render the Fluent theme in a fixed "
"light or dark palette."
msgstr "使用系统/浏览器的偏好设置，或始终以固定的亮色或深色配色渲染 Fluent 主题。"

msgid "Username is required."
msgstr "必须输入用户名。"

msgid "valid HEX color value"
msgstr "有效的十六进制颜色值"

msgid ""
"When enabled, Fluent animations follow the browser or operating system reduced-m"
"otion preference."
msgstr "启用后，Fluent 动画将遵循浏览器或操作系统的减少动态效果偏好设置。"

msgid "Width of the main navigation sidebar in pixels."
msgstr "主导航侧边栏的宽度（像素）。"

msgid "You can create a new token at"
msgstr "您可以在这里创建新的令牌："

msgid "Your theme is up to date!"
msgstr "您的主题已是最新版本！"
